528
00:32:53,870 --> 00:32:56,590
Carlos, just tell me.

529
00:32:56,660 --> 00:32:58,560
I won't be mad.I promise.

530
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:01,120
Gaby, if I was gonna send you flowers,

531
00:33:01,190 --> 00:33:03,030
I wouldn't send you pink roses.

532
00:33:03,600 --> 00:33:05,680
I'd send you white orchids,

533
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:08,090
because I know they're your favorite.

534
00:33:08,850 --> 00:33:12,530
And if I wanted to cheer you up--sunflowers.

535
00:33:12,610 --> 00:33:14,510
And for the flu...

536
00:33:15,340 --> 00:33:17,600
blue irises.

537
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:31,720
