540
00:33:37,180 --> 00:33:38,490
Yeah.

541
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:40,170
That's what dating's for.

542
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:42,100
I know, and it sucks.

543
00:33:42,790 --> 00:33:46,030
