and ate pudding out of a can.

544
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:47,680
It was horrible.

545
00:33:48,720 --> 00:33:51,290
well, if it makes you feel any better,

546
00:33:51,360 --> 00:33:53,710
I dragged to the ballet the other night.

547
00:33:54,530 --> 00:33:57,200
So you are dating.

548
00:33:58,300 --> 00:34:01,500
That's why you've been lifting weights and jogging.

549
00:34:01,600 --> 00:34:06,770
