637
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:13,030
oh, make no mistake,our friendship is over.

638
00:39:18,560 --> 00:39:21,790
- Okay. You go...
- okay.

639
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:34,180
So, winnipeg...must get pretty cold up there.

640
00:39:38,270 --> 00:39:39,750
I'm just getting my coat.

641
00:39:39,830 --> 00:39:42,130
Ian, please, I just lost one of my best friends.

642
00:39:42,210 --> 00:39:43,190
I can't lose you, too.

643
00:39:43,270 --> 00:39:45,070
You said that you wouldn't see him again.

644
00:39:45,110 --> 00:39:49,070
But you had to know that I would go
one more time to just explain everything.

645
00:39:49,110 --> 00:39:50,360
Actually, no, I didn'T.

646
00:39:50,430 --> 00:39:51,800
Well, that's just crazy!

647
00:39:51,880 --> 00:39:53,920
Why are you acting like a crazy person?

648
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:56,610
Because you've already left me once for this--this guy!

649
00:39:56,690 --> 00:39:59,180
Things are different now!
I-I love you!

650
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:01,700
You--you don't have to worry about that anymore.

651
00:40:01,780 --> 00:40:04,040
If we're gonna make this relationship work

652
00:40:04,110 --> 00:40:07,550
then you have to trust me
and why are you smiling at me?

653
00:40:07,630 --> 00:40:09,480
You just said that you love me.

654
00:40:09,560 --> 00:40:10,740
Yeah? So?

655
00:40:10,820 --> 00:40:12,570
Well, you've never said that before.

656
00:40:12,610 --> 00:40:13,750
Yes, I have.

657
00:40:13,820 --> 00:40:15,300
No. I-I-I would've remembered.

658
00:40:15,360 --> 00:40:17,200
