659
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:18,520
Do you have a problem with that?

660
00:40:18,560 --> 00:40:19,600
No, ma'am.

661
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:21,170
You--you--you can't kiss me now.

662
00:40:21,250 --> 00:40:22,000
I'm yelling at you.

663
00:40:22,080 --> 00:40:23,100
Well, I'm listening.

664
00:40:23,180 --> 00:40:26,240
Well...don't--don't think that
you can get out of this,

665
00:40:26,280 --> 00:40:30,840
you know, by just...oh, god. Oh, yeah, uh,

666
00:40:30,930 --> 00:40:33,110
oh, yeah, right--right there.Oh, right there.

