00:40:36,830 --> 00:40:39,700
look, I think we should stop doing thiS.

668
00:40:41,650 --> 00:40:45,890
I know it's my idea,but it just
doesn't feel right anymore.

669
00:40:46,910 --> 00:40:50,130
So you slept with julie.It's no big deal.

670
00:40:50,240 --> 00:40:53,310
Well, it is to her
and I don't want to see her get hurt.

671
00:40:53,390 --> 00:40:54,750
Me, either.

672
00:40:55,520 --> 00:40:58,080
so let's just not tell her.

673
00:41:04,250 --> 00:41:07,430
there's no place in fair view
that's more peaceful.

674
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:09,510
All the floors are hardwood.

675
00:41:09,580 --> 00:41:11,790
Oh, there are brand-new appliances.

676
00:41:11,830 --> 00:41:13,420
And the gardens are...

677
00:41:13,450 --> 00:41:15,020
well, they're beautiful.

678
00:41:15,550 --> 00:41:18,590
So... what do you think?

679
00:41:20,810 --> 00:41:22,470
I'll take it.

680
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:23,830
